{"title":"非典手记","authors":["张庞"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":6,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"非典手记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张庞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人是一个初生的孩子，他的力量，就是生长的力量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——罗宾德拉纳特·泰戈尔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口罩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几层方寸棉纱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"显露出国人坚定的眉眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"防护衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与柔韧的脊梁一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"护送远航的生命之舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"SARS"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几个英文字母"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一夜间让人读懂了许多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔离病室"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个人的空间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满世界的真情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中药罐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满腹的古老神话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煎出了一腔热情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"救护车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声呼啸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载着希望与爱心奔跑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼吸机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以自己的呼吸节奏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延伸人的生命历程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"护士的烛光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点燃一片爱心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮千百生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小汤山医院"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从“提灯女神”进驻这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的名字就和奇迹连在一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"病毒学实验室"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出污泥而不染"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"囿于室而远行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疫情发布会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浸染着每天报纸的版面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发送着一个民族的自信"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}